        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "近迫式急促攔射",
        "title": "近迫式急促攔射",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/25/125391187/52cd1e5b70e7ea798b5a41cd9a51fbef_5800484259799457150.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素戰技</color>\n造成2點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>此技能結算後：</color> <color=#dcdee0>如果我方手牌中含有</color> <color=#ffffff>超量裝藥彈頭</color> <color=#dcdee0>，則</color> <color=#ffffff>捨棄</color> <color=#dcdee0>1張並治療我方受傷最多的角色1點。</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "圓陣擲彈爆轟術",
        "title": "圓陣擲彈爆轟術",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/a36c7a9c9512124baf0b482d8dc69912_3729963044076148809.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n造成2點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> ，在敵方場上生成 <color=#ffffff>二重毀傷彈</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>二重毀傷彈</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n<color=#ffffff>所在陣營切換角色後：</color> 對切換到的角色造成1點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "縱陣武力統籌",
        "title": "縱陣武力統籌",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/4b48c030ba601eab2fe4d2375057a617_6151011494096034807.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>被動技能</color>\n【被動】 <color=#ffffff>敵方角色受到超載反應傷害後：</color> 生成手牌 <color=#ffffff>超量裝藥彈頭（</color> 每回合1次）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "超量裝藥彈頭",
        "title": "超量裝藥彈頭",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2726039240498422525.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>事件牌</color>\n<color=#ffffff>戰鬥行動：</color> 對敵方「出戰角色」造成1點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>此牌被捨棄時：</color> 對敵方「出戰角色」造成1點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/5dca55a012526872199ffb25f0129241_4455298171776218753.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素傷害‧其一",
        "title": "火元素傷害‧其一",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5287058139495960922.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素+</color> <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>融化</color> ：本傷害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>蒸發</color> ：本傷害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超載</color> ：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素傷害‧其二",
        "title": "火元素傷害‧其二",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2999571164676152053.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "附著 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> ，可發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>燃燒</color> ：本傷害+1，召喚 <color=#ffffff>燃燒烈焰</color>\n<color=#ffffff>燃燒烈焰</color>\n<color=#ffd780>召喚物</color>\n<color=#ffffff>結束階段：</color> 造成1點 <color=#ff9999>火元素傷害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_2194847893348258819.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "規則解釋",
        "title": "規則解釋",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/26/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6971972697886981017.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>物理傷害</color>\n物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數</color>\n此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數</color> 耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。\n<color=#ffffff>戰鬥行動</color>\n我方執行了一次戰鬥行動後，會輪到對方行動。\n<color=#ffffff>打出具有此規則的手牌是一個戰鬥行動，而非快速行動。</color>\n<color=#ffffff>捨棄</color>\n透過行動牌或角色技能的效果，將行動牌從手牌或牌庫中棄置。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
    ]
